(6971, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_LOG_MESSAGE_AZ_006', 'The customer has been redirected to ''Checkout Success'' page  after completing payment with offline credit card module selected.'),
(6972, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_INVALID_CC_INFO', 'Please enter the correct credit card information.'),
(6973, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_BUTTON', 'Generate'),
(6974, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_SAVE_KEY_CONFIRMATION_BUTTON', 'Confirm'),
(6975, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_PHP_001', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>IMPORTANT! READ CAREFULLY!</span><p>In accordance to the latest requirements of Visa, MasterCard and other payment systems, shopping cart software uses data encryption to insure the security of credit card information.<p>To activate this module, a pair of RSA keys must be generated including the public key and the private key. This operation is performed only once. The public key is stored on the server and is used for encryption. The private key file, which must be stored on your local machine, is later used to decrypt credit card numbers. The only way to gain access to credit card numbers (i.e. to decrypt them) is by using the private key. Therefore, you must store the private key file in a secure location and make sure it doesn''t get lost.<p>To generate the public and private keys, click the Generate button. After generation is complete, you will be prompted to save the private key file on your computer. Make sure to save this file in a secure location and never lose it! You will need this private key file to access credit card data. In case the private key is lost, NO ONE (including the developers of the shopping cart software) will be able to decrypt the encrypted credit card data.'),
(6976, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_JS_001', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>IMPORTANT! READ CAREFULLY!</span><p>In accordance to the latest requirements of Visa, MasterCard and other payment systems, shopping cart software uses data encryption to insure the security of credit card information.<p>1) No Math library was detected on your server! We strongly recommend installing either GMP or BigIn PHP Math library on your server.<p>The Manual/Offline Credit Card Processing module encrypts credit card data by using the secure 512/1024-bit RSA encryption algorithm. Special mathematical algorithms are used to perform encryption. As a result, to achieve faster generation of encryption and decryption keys one should use one of several Math libraries for PHP - GMP, or BigInt. Having either of these PHP libraries enables performing the encryption and decryption of credit card data in <b>less than one second</b>.<p>In case no Math library is detected, the generation of the public and private keys may take from 5 to 25 minutes; the encryption and decryption of a credit card number during checkout may take 1-3 seconds; and the decryption of credit card data may take 3-5 seconds.<p>To see the list of hosting providers that support Math libraries suitable for encrypting credit card data, please contact Avactis support.<p>2) To activate this module, a pair of RSA keys must be generated including the public key and the private key. This operation is performed only once. The public key is stored on the server and is used for encryption. The private key file, which must be stored on your local machine, is later used to decrypt credit card numbers. The only way to gain access to credit card numbers (i.e. to decrypt them) is by using the private key. Therefore, you must store the private key file in a secure location and make sure it doesn''t get lost.<p>3) To generate the public and private keys, click the Generate button. After generation is complete, you will be prompted to save the private key file on your computer. The key generation process may take from 5 to 25 minutes. Your browser may display messages similar to the one shown here (messages vary depending on the browser). Make sure not to interrupt the key generation process.<div align=''center''><img src=''images/ie6_js_stop_continue_popup.png''></div><p>Make sure to save this file in a secure location and never lose it! You will need this private key file to access credit card data. In case the private key is lost, NO ONE (including the developers of the shopping cart software) will be able to decrypt the encrypted credit card data.'),
(6977, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_002', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>IMPORTANT! READ CAREFULLY!</span><ol><li>The pair of RSA keys has been generated. Your browser window should now pop up a window prompting you to save the private key file.<li>Make sure to save this file in a secure location! The only way to decrypt credit card information is by using this private key!</ol>Please confirm that you have saved the private key file on your local computer. To do so, select the local copy of the file and click Confirm.'),
(6978, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_003', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>IMPORTANT!</span> If you have not saved the private key file on your local machine, you need to generate another pair of RSA keys.'),
(6979, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_004', 'Navigate to the key generation page.'),
(6980, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_005', 'To activate/deactivate the Manual/Offline Credit Card Processing module, select the appropriate status in the Module Status box and then click Save.<p><p>If your private RSA key has been compromised, or if you simply want to replace it with a new one, '),
(6981, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_006', 'navigate to the Key Replacement page.'),
(6982, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_007', 'Download of private RSA key file validated successfully. Please wait while the system saves the public key.'),
(6983, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_GENERATE_KEY_008', 'Problem encountered while validating private key file: the wrong file was uploaded or an error occurred. Please perform key generation again.'),
(6984, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_PHP_001', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>Replacement of data encryption keys.<br>Step 1 of 3 - Generating new key pair.</span><p>After a new pair of keys is generated, all credit card information that is currently encrypted and stored in the online store''s database will be re-encrypted with the new key. You will also need to save the file containing the new private RSA key to your local machine, so that you may be able to decrypt data in the future.<p>To generate new public and private keys, click the Generate button.'),
(6985, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_JS_001', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>Replacement of data encryption keys.<br>Step 1 of 3 - Generating new key pair.</span><p>After a new pair of keys is generated, all credit card information that is currently encrypted and stored in the online store''s database will be re-encrypted with the new key. You will also need to save the file containing the new private RSA key to your local machine, so that you may be able to decrypt data in the future.<p>1) No Math library was detected on your server! We strongly recommend installing either GMP or BigInt PHP Math library on your server.<p>The Manual/Offline Credit Card Processing module encrypts credit card data by using the secure 512/1024-bit RSA encryption algorithm. Special mathematical algorithms are used to perform encryption. As a result, to achieve faster generation of encryption and decryption keys one should use one of several Math libraries for PHP - GMP or BigInt. Having either of these PHP libraries enables performing the encryption and decryption of credit card data in less than one second.<p>In case no Math library is detected, the generation of the public and private keys may take from 5 to 25 minutes (occurs once when this module is activated); the encryption of a credit card number during checkout may take 1-3 seconds; and the decryption of credit card data may take 3-5 seconds.<p>To see the list of hosting providers that support Math libraries suitable for encrypting credit card data, please contact Avactis support.<p>2) To generate the public and private keys, click the Generate button. The key generation process may take from 5 to 25 minutes. Your browser may display messages similar to the one shown here (messages vary depending on the browser). Make sure not to interrupt the key generation process.<p><div align=''center''><img src=''images/ie6_js_stop_continue_popup.png''></div>'),
(6986, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_002', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>Replacement of data encryption keys.<br>Step 2 of 3 - Re-encrypting data using new keys.</span><p>The generation of new keys is complete. The current private key is still valid for accessing credit card information. The new key will become valid only after it is saved to your local hard drive in Step 3.<p>Now you must re-encrypt all encrypted online store data with the new key. To start the re-encryption process, please upload your current private key file and press Start Re-encryption.'),
(6987, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_START_REENCRYPTION_BUTTON', 'Start Re-encryption'),
(6988, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_003', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>Replacement of data encryption keys.<br>Step 3 of 3 - Saving new private key to local machine.<p>IMPORTANT! READ CAREFULLY!</span><p>Re-encryption of credit card info using the new keys is complete. Your browser window should now pop up a window prompting you to save the new private key file. Make sure to save this file in a secure location! The only way to decrypt credit card information is by using this private key! Please confirm that you have saved the new private key file on your local computer; otherwise, the old key will still be valid. To do so, select the local copy of the file with new private key and click Confirm.'),
(6989, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_004', '<span style=''color: rgb(255, 0, 0);''>IMPORTANT!</span> If you did not save the private key file to your local computer, you must re-encrypt the data.'),
(6990, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_005', 'Go to re-encryption page.'),
(6991, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_007', 'Download of private RSA key has been verified successfully. Please wait while the system saves the public key and moves the re-encrypted data.'),
(6992, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_008', 'ERROR: You have uploaded a private RSA key which does not match the system\\''s public key. Decryption of data is impossible. Please upload the correct private key.'),
(6993, 'PM_O_CC', 'MODULE_PAYMENT_OFFLINE_CC_MSG_REPLACE_KEY_009', 'ERROR: You are uploading an empty file. Please upload the correct private RSA key file.');
