(7005, 'PM_PP_CC', 'MODULE_STATUS_FIELD_NAME_DESCR', 'There are two possible statuses for this module - Active and Inactive.<br>If the module status is Active, the module is accessible from the online storefront and its visitors can make payments at checkout.<br>If the module status is Inactive, the module cannot be accessed from the online storefront. In addition, the module is not present in the list of online storefront payment methods displayed at checkout. The Inactive status should be used to temporarily disable accepting payments using the current payment method, or to adjust the appropriate settings.'),
