(7043, 'PM_PP_CC', 'PAYMENT_STATUS_CANCELED_REVERSAL_MSG', 'This means a reversal has been canceled; for example, you, the merchant, won a dispute with the customer and the funds for the transaction that was reversed have been returned to you.'),
