(7053, 'PM_PP_CC', 'PAYMENT_STATUS_PENDING_MULTI_CURRENCY_MSG', 'You do not have a balance in the currency sent, and you do not have your Payment Receiving Preferences set to automatically convert and accept this payment. You must manually accept or deny this payment.'),
